---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../consts';
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use" description="Terms and conditions for using MoveWell Reviews.">
  <article class="container legal">
    <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</p>
    <p class="notice">This page is a starting template, not legal advice — have a qualified attorney review it before launch.</p>

    <h2>Acceptance of terms</h2>
    <p>
      By accessing {SITE.domain}, you agree to these Terms of Use. If you don't agree, please
      don't use the site.
    </p>

    <h2>Editorial content, not professional advice</h2>
    <p>
      Content on this site — including reviews, ratings, and buying guides — reflects our own
      opinions based on hands-on testing and research. It is provided for general informational
      purposes only and is not medical, fitness, or professional advice. Consult a qualified
      professional before starting any exercise or recovery routine, especially if you have a
      pre-existing health condition.
    </p>

    <h2>Accuracy &amp; changes</h2>
    <p>
      Product specifications, availability, and pricing change frequently and are controlled by
      the retailers we link to, not by us. We try to keep information current but make no
      guarantee of accuracy at the time you read it — always verify details on the merchant's
      site before purchasing.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
    <p>
      This site contains affiliate links; see our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for details.
    </p>

    <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
    <p>
      Unless otherwise noted, text, graphics, and original photography on this site are owned by
      {SITE.name}. Product images/trademarks belong to their respective owners and are used for
      identification purposes under fair use.
    </p>

    <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>
      {SITE.name} is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. To the fullest extent
      permitted by law, we are not liable for any damages arising from your use of this site or
      reliance on its content, including purchase decisions made based on our reviews.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-party sites</h2>
    <p>
      We are not responsible for the content, policies, or practices of third-party sites you
      reach through links on {SITE.domain}.
    </p>

    <h2>Governing law</h2>
    <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the United States, without regard to conflict-of-law principles.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may revise these terms at any time; continued use of the site means you accept the revised terms.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Reach us at <a href={`mailto:${SITE.contactEmail}`}>{SITE.contactEmail}</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal { padding: 40px 24px 70px; max-width: 720px; }
  .updated { color: #888; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  .notice { background: #fff8e6; border: 1px solid #f0d78c; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; font-size: 0.85rem; }
  h2 { margin-top: 30px; }
</style>
